" Add the g flag to search/replace by default
" From vim.wikia.com:
" > Using :set gdefault creates confusion because then %s/// is global,
" > whereas %s///g is not (that is, g reverses its meaning)
" > CONCLUSION: DO NOT SET IT AS DEFAULT
